{"tid":90855,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發現都幾多人唔知上年6月修訂嘅新球例","createTime":"2017-01-22T12:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T13:07:00.000Z","uid":319,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21624161fb2eb0f1ef68d4a838ffbaa1ac1f59e5","tid":90855,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"最後的防守球員犯規無須紅牌被逐<br />\n<br />\n根據以往的球例，假如進攻一方呈單刀之勢，然後防守一方的最後一名防守球員以犯規的方式阻止對方進球，可能會出現三重判罰：紅牌、12碼以至往後的自動停賽3場。<br />\n<br />\n不過，修訂球例後，最後的防守球員犯規將不會自動判為紅牌，假如球証認為犯規動作並不嚴重，以黃牌警告即可。"},{"pid":"3ebbaa9ac0b2414c484ceafa158b4f50ee8adb53","tid":90855,"uid":3577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:19:48.000Z","msg":"未必全餐丫嘛<br />\n 知啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c862e0ccf90986fbfc264a1afef7e8a01485d61","tid":90855,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未必全餐丫嘛<br />\n 知啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你知姐 有人唔知㗎嘛<br />\n<br />\n我成日都仲見到好多人話拉跌單刀嘅人一定要直紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918a2182521ba3cd69d349febb4227aa3a570dbc","tid":90855,"uid":5827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:26:03.000Z","msg":"龍門算最後一個定個後衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910af00d15c0124ffe88abad62877a7d4a50c089","tid":90855,"uid":13088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"咁12碼呢？"},{"pid":"bbe828edcceb2a570d869cd3fae5e377c1894c95","tid":90855,"uid":13088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:27:47.000Z","msg":"將不會自動判為紅牌，<br />\n<br />\n由一定變做唔一定<br />\n<br />\n唔係由一定變做唔會"},{"pid":"0cb04e8e007c0229349d05ea924c400cf2a1c4ea","tid":90855,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將不會自動判為紅牌，<br />\n<b